Package: tinyelf
Title: Audit R Shared Libraries for Portability
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Troy", "Hernandez", email = "troy@cornball.ai",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-4248-604X"))
Description: Audits R package shared libraries (.so files) for portability
    issues on Linux. Checks GLIBC symbol version requirements, unexpected
    system library dependencies, and hardcoded build paths in rpath/runpath
    entries. Inspired by Python's auditwheel. Zero dependencies, base R only.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/cornball-ai/tinyelf
BugReports: https://github.com/cornball-ai/tinyelf/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
OS_type: unix
Suggests:
    tinytest,
    tinyrox
